(8441, 143607, '野樂府', '冷與暖的對持.電音融和中國風.編制出絕美的風華\r\n\r\nCounter between hot and cold.\r\nCorespond with China and eletronic.\r\nWeave out the bravery tune.', '2015-03-09 00:00:00', 0, 2, 7, '野樂府', '', 0, '', 0, 0, '2015-03-11 14:28:02', '2015-03-11 15:00:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
